column2: I would rather have someone else do it if it's something that absolutely needs doing.{nl}Why does it always have to be me?
The demons and monsters are still at large...{nl}At least we don't have to worry about being robbed by highwaymen.{nl}That is if we can make it out alive.
You go out scouting for days then you have to write up a report for days more!{nl}Can we get anything done in this state?
I'm here to assist Tadas.{nl}I'm not here to clean up after Wolke's mess.
I've tricked Kartas and prevented him from stealing the Seed of the Divine Tree.{nl}If I could break away from these seals, I would be able to recover on my own.
Why would Kartas go so far as to imprison me under this barrier...{nl}Does he really know the properties of this seed...?
I'm going to find Miss Neringa as soon as I feel a little better.{nl}I'm sure she will know a way for us to rescue Master Medeina from Kartas.
Revelator! There's an evil barrier surrounding the forest, it's dangerous in here!{nl}Please, you have to go!
We're trapped inside Kartas' barrier, and Master Medeina's powers aren't enough to break it.{nl}We need to help her regain her strength...
If Kartas finds us, we'll be in great danger.{nl}Please, help Master Medeina recover.
I'm glad Ilona is safe at least, despite the barrier.{nl}Revelator, please look for a way to deactivate the barrier.
Take Ilona and find Master Medeina.
Her footprints stop here. Should we look inside the courtyard?
Oh, I'm so glad Master Medeina is safe!{nl}That Teleportation Magic Circle needs to be destroyed...
Revelator, please destroy the magic circle.{nl}This might be the only chance we get while Kartas is gone.
Master Medeina's barrier is finally gone.{nl}We should hurry now...
Overloading the second magic circle worked!
Oh... Master Medeina...
She...
I was too late...
Although Master Medeina was taken by Kartas...{nl}Your precious help will always be remembered, Revelator.{nl}

Wait, could it be...are you the Revelator?
We are in grave danger.{nl}Ever since Medzio Diena, the dimension started collapsing from time to time.

The monsters nearby accelerate the collapse.{nl}This will spread to the whole continent if not prevented beforehand.{nl} I need the help of the Revelator as it is a matter beyond my power.{nl} Please, lend me a hand.
Be careful not to get swept into the dimensional collapse.{nl} It would be wise to approach when you're fully prepared.
Prevent the dimension from collapsing
That's correct.
Not really.
Talk to the Sage Envoy.
The Sage Envoy at the Fallen City is providing Revelators something. Talk to the Sage Envoy.
We are investigating a recent severe cold wave that happened here.{nl}
Three investigations revealed that the demons beneath this cliff were responsible for the severe cold wave.{nl}
Demon's name is..{nl}
Glacia.{nl}
It was a demon called Glacia.{nl}We also found a black crystal floating on a special device.{nl}Not sure what it is, but it was condensing strong magical power.{nl}
Several attempts were made to defeat Glacia, but they failed to break through the cold wave and the demons.{nl}
I heard about the Revelators activities.{nl}Please help defeating the Glacia.
Well, I'll see you again when you are ready to go down the cliff.
If you go down the cliff, it will be hard to ask for additional support.{nl}It won't be easy to break through the cold wave generated by Glacia.{nl}
We will be here to help the Revelator ride the cage and descend safely down the cliff.{nl}
I am counting on you about the Glacia.
Revelator.{nl}Would you mind taking a moment?{nl}
Last time, while researching the bottom of the cliff, I found a few things.{nl}Among them, this red liquid..{nl}It wasn't freezing in the cold, it only had thin ice on it.{nl}
I collected it since it seemed so peculiar.{nl}If there is anyone you could trust to analyze, I will leave it to you, Revelator.
Thank you.{nl}Please come back to me when the analysis is complete.
Are you saying that you want to analyze the solution? {nl}It's not difficult to do, but I feel ominous about it.
I need a plant to make sure.{nl}I don't care what it is, so can you get me one from nearby?{nl}After all, lengthy plants are growing not far from here.
Please come back to me when the analysis is complete.
This..{nl}
seems to be Kruvina.{nl}I have heard about it from the rumor.{nl}It's in the form of a liquid, but... It's the first time I actually saw it.{nl}
However, there is more blood mixed here.{nl}I think... someone vomited this with blood from their body.{nl}
For example, It may be the demon Glacia like you said.{nl}
It's a bad sign.
We ask that you investigate this with responsibility.{nl}Something like this, not only the ordinary demon will desire for it.
You're back.{nl}
Alright.{nl}We will take care of the process and investigation of this solution. {nl}Thank you very much for your help.
Revelator.{nl}I heard of a story about a mysterious woman witnessed among soldiers in a camp on the Stogas Plateau.
I received orders to maintain my current position. {nl}As the investigation wasn't reported to the Master, I don't think I can move.{nl}Could you meet the camp soldiers instead of me?
Thank you for your help.{nl}If you look for Stogas Commanding Officer Ades in the camp, you'll be able to save your effort.
Did you come after hearing an eyewitness about a mysterious woman?

I totally remember.{nl}Strange thing was, she was crying for help but she seemed to be ignoring us when we tried to help her.{nl}Also, she muttered that no one was helping her.{nl}She seemed like she was out of her mind.
If it's hard to understand, ask Mortimer.{nl}He was the one who found her.
If you look for Stogas Commanding Officer Ades in the camp, you'll be able to save your effort.
Yes? What is it?{nl}
Ask Soldier Motimer about the woman.{nl} He was the one who found her.
Your asking about the woman.
Oh, but it's not a good time.{nl}I am in a hurry.{nl}While I'm finishing my job, you might look at the road to the Gehima Empty Lot.{nl}It was around there, where I first found the woman.
I'll get the work done in a hurry, so please check out the roads of the Gehima Empty Lot first.
I'll get the work done in a hurry, so check out the roads of the Gehima Empty Lot first.
I was looking for you, Revelator.
That shackle..{nl}It is the shackle from the woman.

She was staring at the air and asked for help as if she couldn't see or hear us at all.{nl}I was trying to help, but I couldn't.{nl}She moved toward Second Almol Work Place muttering that no one was helping her.

It seemed difficult to survive on this location.{nl}Come to think of it, her eyes staring in the air were strange.{nl} I think there weren't any black parts of the pupil.{nl} Taking steps seemed to be difficult for her, so breaking the shackle was all I could do.
You're here.{nl}Have you finished the investigation about the woman witnessed at the camp?
So that's what happened.{nl}It is very likely that she has come up to this place and fell down the cliff.{nl}She may not be safe for sure.
Kruvina Liquid was on the fallen object means...that the woman must be the Glacia.
Based on what the Revelator has investigated and what we've been investigating, it seems that Glacia was harmed by a larger being.{nl}There must be a demon behind this that harmed her.
Revelator.{nl}I think it's time to go down the cliff.{nl}Tell me whatever you find at the White Witch's Forest.
Glacia might have become this state after she fell off the cliff.{nl} Tell me whatever you find at the White Witch's Forest.
Revelator for now..
Stop, please.
Revelator.{nl} I need to tell you something.
I am the commander here.{nl}Please refrain from any unauthorized investigation activities.{nl}Even if you are a revelator, you will be at a disadvantage if you break the laws of the Kingdom.

I would like to say my sincere appreciation for the dedication of the Revelator who cooperated with the investigation.{nl}However, if any enemy is a threat to the new world, he must be punished.{nl}That's the only duty for the Crusader.
Please refrain from arbitrary investigation from now on.
We are investigating the abnormal severe cold wave coming from the Nubarsk Cliff.{nl}However, we are having difficulties due to insufficient manpower.{nl}If you are okay, can you help me?
Thank you.{nl} Let's go to the Nubarsk Cliff.
Abnormal severe cold wave is coming from Nubarsk Cliff.
Thank you for helping the investigation.{nl}If enough evidence is gathered, I will take it to the kingdom and prepare for plans.{nl}I'm worried about the lack of manpower all the time.
I can't help you.
White Witch and the Crusader(1)
I am busy with other things right now.
White Witch and the Crusader(2)
I'll do my best on this task.
I want to quit.
White Witch and the Crusader(3)
I don't want to be involved anymore.
White Witch and the Crusader(4)
I am not interested.
White Witch and the Crusader(5)
Share the result of the investigation.
The investigation is not finished yet.
White Witch and the Crusader(6)
I have other things to do.
White Witch and the Crusader(7)
Show the letter.
Pretend not to know.
Abnormal Severe Cold Wave of Stogas Plateau
Help with the investigation.
Don't help with the investigation.
Talk to Crusader Master

The Crusaders Master, who was in charge of investigations in the Stogas Plateau, is asking for help from the Revelators.{nl}Go to Zofija Eleonora, Crusader Master of Stogas Plateau and listen to the story.
Get ready and go back to Crusader Master
It is said that Zofija had asked the Revelators for help in defeating the Glacia under the cliff.{nl}If you're ready to go down the cliff,  Return to Zofija and tell about it.
White Witch and the Crusader
Talk to Crusader Envoy
The Crusader Envoy seems to have something to tell you.{nl}Talk to the Crusader Envoy.
Collect Plants.
The Crusader instructed an investigation about the objects found during the exploration of the White Witch's Forest.{nl}Go to Plague Doctor Master and ask for an analysis of Red Liquid with Thin Ice.
Return to Plague Doctor Master
You have acquired the plant Plague Doctor Master asked for.{nl}Return to Plague Doctor Master and hand over the plant to finish analysis of the solution.
Receive the result of investigation from Plague Doctor Master
Talk to the Plague Doctor again.
The Plague Doctor Master expressed concern that the identity of the solution was Kruvina's Liquid.{nl}He seems to have something to request, so talk to the Plague Doctor Master again.
Return to Crusader Envoy.
Finished analysis of the solution.{nl}Return to Crusader Envoy and return the Kruvina Liquid.
Crusader Envoy said they would take up further investigations of the Kruvina Liquid.{nl}Talk to the Envoy again to ask if there is anything to help.
Stogas Commanding Officer Ades
The Crusader Envoy says there is a place where a figure suspected to be Glacia has been spotted.{nl}Go to Stogas Commanding Officer Ades at Stogas Plateau camping ground and listen to him.
Go to Soldier Motimer.
I heard the story of a woman who is suspected to be a Glacia from Ades.{nl}Go to Soldier Motimer for more details.{nl}
Talk to Soldier Motimer.
Listen to Soldier Motimer about a story of a woman who is suspected to be a Glacia.
Investigate incident place.
Investigate the place where the woman was found while Soldier Motimer completes his task.
Return to Soldier Motimer.

I found the Krubina Liquid at the scene of the incident, and I was able to find the shackle from the monsters.{nl}Go back to Soldier Motimer and show the results of the investigation and ask about the circumstances of the incident.
Retrieve Lost Objects
Hand over worn out shackle to Crusader Envoy
Finished investigation from the camping ground.{nl}Return to Crusader Envoy and tell the result of the investigation.
Talk to the Crusader Envoy to continue the investigation.
Conduct an investigation in the White Witch's Forest.
The Crusader Envoy guessed that there would be someone behind this.{nl}Investigate the Glacia's traces in the White Witch's Forest.
Deliver bunch of letters to Crusader Envoy.
Bring the Crusader Envoy items from the White Witch's Forest.
Talk to Crusader Master
Crusader Master Zofija Eleanora seems to have something to say. {nl}Talk to her.
Find Crusader Envoy.
Find Crusader Envoy who is investigating the abnormal severe cold wave of Stogas Plateau.
Investigate the abnormal severe cold wave coming from Nubarsk Cliff.
Investigate the abnormal severe cold wave coming from Nubarsk Cliff and tell about it to Crusader Envoy.
Tell Crusader Envoy about the investigation result of abnormal severe cold wave.
You came.{nl}I asked you for cooperation.
Since you have investigated about the Glacia, I think you are the one who knows the best about the truth.{nl}Will you cooperate with the investigation?
Thank you for your cooperation.{nl}The thing I gave you is the accessory from the Glacia's Cloth.{nl}We need to investigate how the Glacia could have survived from the demon and be here.
Please show that accessory to the demon and see how they react.
Thank you for your cooperation.{nl}Show shining marvel to the demon and see how they react.
You are back.
The demons were frightened away?{nl}It is true that the Glacia is a strong demon.. She might have been a human when she was passing here.
Then.. Maybe more than the Glacia might be related to this case.
Our last Envoy said that he have seen Suspicious Piece with Kruvina Liquid on near the root on the rock.{nl}We haven't touched a thing to preserve the scene.
I'll investigate for the piece, so please look for the Suspicious Piece and prepare for the investigation.
Go down the stairs to the left, and keep going, the Suspicious Piece is between the rock wall and the tree roots.{nl}Revelator, please go first and prepare for the investigation.
How should I tell...{nl}To start with the conclusion..
This piece has the power of demons over long years{nl}This is more of a power I have ever encountered.{nl}Maybe the Glacia is...
Would you believe that Glacia is no matter anymore compared to the master of power?
Investigation is in fast progress thanks to the Revelator's cooperation.
Inconveniently.. We need more convincing evidence to prove who or what is behind Glacia.
Did you say that the place where you found Glacier's letter last time was under the cliff?{nl}I would like you to go there and check again to see if there is any evidence that I missed at that time.
Please investigate the White Witch's Forest.
Instruction is definitely proof.{nl}It even has the name of Glacia.
But how come is it written in the language of humans? The power felt from the piece was definitely the power of the demon.
It wants to speak of its presence.
Now the proof that someone is behind is for sure.{nl}Revelator, while you were down the cliff, I have requested fora cooperation to the Kingdom.

It is said that there is a person in the kingdom who knows best when it comes to the power of the demons. {nl}Please give the Rangda master Uolios Wahid the pieces.{nl}Undesirable.. but it is an order from the Kingdom.
We're counting on you.{nl}If you pass that piece, there is no more thing left that you need to help.
Revelator, thank you for your help.
Glacia Casimila.{nl}It's Glacia's human name.
You came.{nl}Already heard about the story.
Strong energy.{nl}Had it not been for the Crusader Master's action, it would not have been strange if you fell down on your way to this place.

The owner of this power is the name of the land, given by the name of the Beholder.{nl}I will tell you more than this later if I have a chance.{nl}We'll take care of this piece.{nl}Will you hand it over to the girl next to you?
Rangda Girl
Treat her well, she is a kid.
Be careful not to lose your life getting involved in Dimensional Collapse and Division Singularity.{nl}Especially, behave carefully in the Division Singularity. It is an extremely dangerous place.
column5: Be careful not to get swept into the dimensional collapse.{nl} It would be wise to approach when you're fully prepared.

column2: If you're not ready enough, don't get any closer. Be ready thoroughly before approaching.

Cooperate with the investigation.
Won't cooperate with the investigation.

I'd be prepared.
Tell him to go there later

That's too difficult to do now.

I will pass it.
I can't help you.

I don't want to be involved anymore.
Find Crusader Master.
Crusader Master seems to have something to say to you.{nl}Go to her and ask her what's wrong.
Use Glacia's belongings to the monster.
As the Crusader Master asked, show Glacia's belongings to the monsters.
Report the result of investigation to the Crusader Master.
Monsters frightened away as you show the belongings of the Glacia!{nl}Tell the result of the investigation.
Crusader Master is trying to ask for cooperation for the next investigation.{nl}Talk to the Crusader Master.
Prepare for the Suspicious Piece.

The Crusader Master has received a report from the envoy about the Suspicious Piece that is believed to have been spilled by Glacier.{nl}Go to the Suspicious Piece and be prepared in advance for the Crusader Master to investigate.
Return to Crusader Master.
Crusader Master took the Suspicious Piece.{nl}Retur to her and hear about the result of the investigation.
Ask the Crusader Master what is needs for the next investigation.
Conduct an investigation in the White Witch's Forest(Legend).
The Crusader Master says that more convincing evidence is needed to identify the existence of the demons behind Glacier.{nl}Go back to the White Witch's Forest and look at the Worn Out Pouch.
Show Crusader Master the Mysterious Order you've found from the Worn Out Pouch.
Ask Crusader Master if more help is needed.
Go to Rangda Master.

The Crusader Master thanked for cooperating with the investigation, and finally asked to visit the Rangda Master to do a thorough investigation on the Suspicious Sculpture.{nl}Go to the Rangda Master in Saalus Convent and ask about the Suspicious Sculpture.
Talk to Rangda Master.
Hear opinions about the suspicious sculpture from the Langda Master.
Hand over the Suspicious Sculpture to Rangda Girl.

I heard the explanation of the Suspicious Sculpture from the Rangda Master.{nl}Because it is dangerous we have to entrust this sculpture to Rangda, who is more skilled in dealing with the power of the demons.{nl}Please hand over the sculpture to the Rangda Girl.
Although we have removed all Mirtinas in Issaugoti Forest, Mirtinas collected by Beholder would be left.{nl}Baubas and Baiga are still seeking Mirtinas.
Mirtinas in the whole area of Orsha isn't completely removed,{nl}demons must return.
So Revelator,{nl}this precarious peace will strike Orsha again in the near future.
Be fully prepared for the threat.{nl}By taking the fate you bear as a lesson.
The forest in front is called Issaugoti Forest.
In the Issaugoti forest, I can feel the most powerful energy of Mirtinas than any other part of the forest.
There must be Mirtinas mined by the Beholder's demon there.{nl}Lot of demons must be dominating that place.
Beholder always moved with plans.{nl}He must have set preparation of Mirtinas storage.
If heading for the Issaugoti Forest without thinking will make you take a big risk.
Beholder's demon must have already stored a lot of Mirtinas.{nl}It's hard to remove all at once with your power..
I am worried that moving Mirtinas with my power may crash with the power inside the Mirtinas.{nl}Besides demons will notice my energy soon.
Human's Bomb will be suitable to remove Mirtinas as soon and as many as possible.
Can you get the Bombs?
Lord of Orsha told to ask for help when needed?{nl}It's a good thing.{nl}I just hope there's a suitable Bomb for Orsha.
[Lord of Orsha]Inesa Hamondale
You need the help of Orsha?{nl}I am the one who asked for help, so I'll give whatever that can be helpful.
You need a bomb.{nl}Bombs will be in the Armaments Storage.{nl}I'll order the guard to get it.
I hope this has enough power as you wish..
Please handle carefully.{nl}This is a magic bomb with very strong power.
You may be caught into the explosion, so please be careful.{nl}You must activate it after you evade yourself into safe area.
Be careful as much as you can, Revelator.{nl}Thank you for fighting for Orsha.
Hurry up.{nl}For the Orsha where you have to protect.
You came.{nl}Is that the Bomb Lord of Orsha gave?
I see.{nl}We have found a way to destroy Mirtinas, so we only need to access it.
Beholder, Ragana, Baiga..{nl}Three demons are fighting with different purpose.
Therefore, we will use their desire.{nl}Use suggestion Ragana and Baiga made e to Revelator in reverse and give them false information.

Then Ragana's force and Baiga's force will conflict, and Beholder's force won't just watch.{nl} Take advantage of the confusion on the battlefield and approach the Mirtinas.{nl}We'll move together to the Issaugoti Forest, but if I move hastily, it won't be useful to turn the demons' eyes.
As you know, we can't move together.
I'll see if there is another Mirtinas storage near Orsha.
Don't forget.{nl}Finding the location of the Mirtinas is first rather than the force of Baiga and Ragana.
Please move quietly but quickly so that the demons won't notice.
Be careful not to get caught up in the force struggle of the demons.
Have you find a place where seems to be the Mirtinas Storage?
Fortunately, it doesn't seems like there is another Mirtinas Storage besides here near Orsha.
As expected..{nl}The demons' guards are extraordinary as expected.
As planned, let's use the demons of Ragana's force and Baiga's force.
It might be good to lure the demons to the area with enough space.{nl}If it's too far from the storage, the Beholder's demons might not move.{nl}Please find a suitable place.
Have you find it?{nl}You mean the Planas Lot.
There won't be a problem in that area.
Meet the Ragana's messenger first.{nl}I can feel the presence of Ragana's power in the Praeiti Shelter.{nl}Ragana's messenger will be there who she told.{nl}Give the messenger false information.
The false information can be told that there is a Mirtinas Storage mined by the Beholder's demon in the Planas Lot.
And please give the same information to the Baiga's messenger in the Mesalas Camping Ground.
Ragana's Messenger
Hmm..{nl}Seems to be true.
I'll give this information to Ragana.{nl}Ragana is endlessly merciful to loyalty ones.{nl}You must be available to have the Ragana's grace.
Wise choice.
If you arouse the fight after giving false information to the Ragana and Baiga's messenger,{nl}it might avert the demons' eyes in the Mirtinas Storage.{nl}Please hurry up.
Hmm..{nl}Hmm..
Okay.{nl}I'll tell Baiga what you've said.{nl}However, you'd better not hold your head high.
Baiga doesn't like arrogant human..
Good work.{nl}We only need to wait for the demons' reaction to the false information.
While the demons who have responded are catching their eyes, access the Mirtinas.{nl}Leave when you're ready.
When the bombs explode, demons will look for you even in the confusion.{nl}It might be the cause for demons attacking the Orsha.
Demons must pass here to head for the Orsha,{nl}and I have to retrieve the Mirtinas from the demons..
There is a reason for me to defeat the demons heading forthe Orsha.
Move for your mission.

Both Ragana and Baiga are demons with high self-esteem.{nl}If they notice that you've fooled them, they won't leave Revelator alone.{nl}Don't try to fight with them.{nl}There is going to be an obvious chance later.
Demon God Raga
I was waiting for you.{nl}Kid of Laima.
Excellent!{nl}I wondered how much a fragile human could do.
You've blown up the Beholder's Mirtinas?}{nl}I'm proud of you.
You trying to fool me is unforgivable, but..{nl}you've blown up the Mirtinas collected by the Beholder, so I'll move on this time.
By the way, Beholder won't leave you alone..{nl}If you want to live, escape towards the downwards.{nl}Go on,{nl}don't get killed by Beholder without my permission.
Finally found it.{nl}Revelator.
Are you be ready to die?{nl}You should fully pay for deceiving me .
You're back.{nl}I've definitely heard the explosion sound of the bomb.
You've met Baubas?
Demon God Baubas..
Now that Giltine is gone, Baubas is the strongest being among the Demon Gods.{nl}The fact that Baubas saved Baiga means that the relationship between the two is easier than we've thought.
It's not happy news, but if it were not for Baubas, you would have got huge damage from the Beholder..{nl}It could've been worse.
Anyway, it's time to finish your mission.{nl}Go to Orsha and meet the Lord.{nl}Demons of Ragana, Baiga, and the Beholder's force are certainly discouraged.
The situation is not completely over yet,{nl}but will be looking forward to hear this news.
You are back.{nl}I assumed that it was Revelator since I heard the loud explosion sound.
I'm glad you seem okay.
I see.{nl}Orsha was helped by the Revelator once again.
Thank you on behalf of Orsha and province of Kiren.{nl}At least the Orsha has earned some time to prepare for the next battle.
Many people have been injured and collapsed, but we won't sit back.{nl}After saving the people who haven't evacuated{nl}time for counterattack will come.
Thank you again to the Revelator.
Demons won't directly attack the Orsha for now.
But Revelator, you know well that this precarious peace won't stay long.
You've been faithful to your duty to protect Orsha.{nl}I was also responsible enough.
Out of my sight!
Thank you for coming.{nl}Orsha is in danger.
Powerful enemies that never seen appeared before suddenly invaded the entire province of Kiren.{nl}To protect the Orsha and the nearby, I asked for help to
Revelator active all over the continent and you.{nl}Please help and fight for the Orsha.
Thank you for helping.{nl}Orsha where ancestors of the family have kept with their lives, will now be protected by us.

However, before that, there is someone who is looking for you.{nl}Go to the Laima's Sanctuary via Statue of Goddess Ausrine and the one will be waiting for you.{nl}The one said only you could be there.
Nice to meet you.{nl}Revelator.
I'm not comfortable to meet you at a time like this.{nl}War cloud in Orsha is extending their hands across the continent to the world.

The reason I called you is because of the fact that both you and I have the responsibility on this incident.{nl}I'll talk about the details in Lemprasa Pond.{nl}If you are ready, I'll be waiting at the Lemprasa Pond.
You are ready.{nl}I'll be waiting at the Lemprasa Pond.
You are here.{nl}To tell you about our responsibility..

In the past Kruvina incident in this area, I was captured by Demon Lord Zaura, {nl}and that's when a powerful Kruvina was created with my life power.{nl}And you saw on the last journey that the Beholder had some of it.
It may sound unreasonable,{nl}but we are the only ones who can see the main culprit of this situation
But we need to be a little more certain if this is a clear move of the Beholder.{nl}Could you get some helpful information from the demons around?
I'll tell you more details after figuring out the situation.
Please find some evidence related to the Beholder from the demons nearby.
Do you mean that demons have the ore with evil magic?
You've obviously seen the Beholder taking this ore through chaos.
But how can the demons have this ore which can come out from the chaos..
Anyway I need to find where demons had this ore.{nl}It may be found through the demons' memory.
Randoluma Rest Place won't draw big attention.
It's not enough but I've seen the trace of Beholder through demons' memory.{nl}But it is insufficient to be sure.
The identity of ore is yet clear.
Let's try again.{nl}More memory might be readable by purifying the demons' spirit with Divine Energy.
I'll share my power with you.{nl}The spirit of demons will be purified and guided to me if you use my blessing to the demons in the Adata Highway.
I'll go to the Adata Highway first and open the power.
Fortunately, the identity of ore became clear.{nl}The name of ore is Mirtinas..{nl}Beholder called this evil ore like that.
Revelator,{nl}Beholder is trying to destroy the world..{nl}precisely the Divine Tree with the Mirtinas.
Mirtinas is a Magic Source comparable with the Belorb.{nl}Giltine stopped the supply of Belorb and flooded the Divine Tree.
On other hand..{nl}If Beholder supplies Mirtinas endlessly, the world will rote with Root of Divin Tree and will turn to a horrible world.{nl}If the amount of Mirtinas is enough.
I have seen an extraordinary crevice in the Malkos Felled Area from the demon's memory.{nl}Mirtinas might came from that crevice.
I'll check the way to the Woods of the Linked Bridges{nl}Please check the Malkos Felled Area.{nl}I'll see you in the Woods of the Linked Bridges.
I was waiting for you.
Are you saying that this was really on the forehead of the demons like a horn?
This is Kruvina.
But it's a bit different.{nl}Do you think this can spurt through the body?{nl}Demon Lord Zaura created Kruvina through me also had help from the device.
Kruvina turns human into demon.
You've also seen a kid turning after using Kruvina.
I can feel my life power from this Kruvina.{nl}Maybe Beholder used Kruvina created through me to turn human into a demon.{nl}This is why I should be responsible for this situation.
Every residents in Orsha might turn into demons.{nl}You need to save the Orsha, so we are heading in same direction.
We just have the same direction, and keep in mind that we are moving for each of our own responsibility.
If I help you, Ausrine won't just sit back.
This is a passage connecting to the Lemprasa Pond where you've just passed.{nl}Demons who rally to hunt down the Mirtinas and attack Orsha is dominating the Woods of the Linked Bridges.
I need to retrieve the Mirtinas which demons are mining.{nl}What will you do?
You are understanding right.{nl}Then, will see you later.
I saw the residents of Orsha entering the village safely, who couldn't escape while you were dealing with demons.
You are doing your mission excellently.{nl}I also could retrieve some of Mirtinas.
I am going to go to the deeper area of the Woods of the Linked Bridge to continuously retrieve Mirtinas.
Gyvenimo Crossroads near here has the crevice which demons used to mine the Mirtinas.{nl}Unlike the crevice you've seen in the Lemprasa Pond, it isn't worth investigation because it is hard.
This is the only way to the Woods of the Linked Bridges, and the demons are occupying.
I've stopped here feeling the magic.{nl}It is definitely the magic of Beholder.
It is just an assumption, but I guess the demons surely need this magic to mine the Mirtinas.{nl}In other words if we can find and destroy the source of magic, we can stop the Mirtinas mining.
If that happens we can prevent Mirtinas from getting in hands of Beholder.{nl}And also damage the demons rallied to attack the Orsha.
I am going to find the source of magic.{nl}I'll seek in the cliffs where humans like you can't fly to.
Seems like Goddess Lada has dropped the blessing by purpose{nl}Search for the source of magic in Morku Farm by using the blessing.
Found the Beholder's Black Crystal which is the source of magic{nl}Check if it can be destroyed
Let's use Goddess Lada's Blessing.
Liquid in the crevice is still boiling
Will you investigate the crevice?
I can still feel the magic permeating in the crevice{nl}Go to the Bonan Forest Road direction and look for the Beholder's Black Crystal
Will you attack the Beholder's Black Crystal?
There were lots of Crystals besides two Black Crystal you've found.{nl}Destroyed all of the Crystals in the Woods of the Linked Bridges.
Mirtinas crevices in the Woods of the Linked Bridges are all harden.
However{nl}There must be Mirtinas which demons have mined,{nl}but none of Mirtinas was found.
That Mirtinas cannot get in to Beholder's hands.{nl}I have to find the storage and retrieve the Mirtinas.
Revelator,{nl}you also have thing to do.
Find the Goddess Lada in Paupys Crossing.
I've chased the Beholder but waited for you after looking at this place.
Have you noticed?{nl}Beholder isn't the only one who has invaded Orsha.{nl}Even two powers of demons makes three forces who invaded the Orsha including the Beholder.
But it is obvious that all of their purposes is the Mirtinas.{nl}They are demons of each Demon King Kartas and Demon God Ragana.
However, we can't be sure.{nl}Especially, I can't believe that Demon King Kartas is facing against Demon God Ragana.
There may be another being who controls them.
First, we need to find the real superior who moves the servants of Demon King Kartas.{nl}Can you handle those demons who invaded Orsha?
Thank you for understanding the situation.
I also will find who is after the Mirtinas.
See you again here.
Defeat the Vynmedis and get the symbol of superior
These are Token of Baiga and Ragana..{nl}Are you saying that the demons of Kartas were having the Token of Baiga?
Demon King Kartas won't resist Ragana..{nl}But maybe Baiga can.
Demon King Baiga has been in close cooperation with Demon God Baubas for a long time.{nl}Demon God Baubas must be the strongest demon without Giltine at this moment.
I can realize again that it's a world where Giltine has disappeared.
Demons of Baiga were obviously after Mirtinas.{nl}It is strange that demons of Ragana only tried to interrupt mining the Mirtinas, and there were no circumstances of them being after the Mirtinas.
Anyway besides their purpose, it won't be good for both human and Goddess if the demon becomes the owner of Mirtinas.{nl}We should hurry to find the Mirtinas Storage.
It is just that strong demons are raging from every direction since coming in here.{nl}It's not clear if it is a Beholder's Black Crystal, or another existence equivalent to it.
You are the pawn of Laima.
To be honest, I was surprised.{nl}Even though Laima helped, it may be said as a talent that human has driven Giltine to the corner.
Are you curious about why I came here?
Root of the Divine Tree isn't a thing that you should care.
The world you know is not even a grain of the existing world.{nl}Mortal human which will die in a momentary life has an arrogant curiosity.
Never mind.
You've met Baiga.{nl}I was so focused on chasing Ragana that I noticed the presence of Baiga belatedly.
In case of Ragana,{nl}I couldn't chase her because it was near impossible chasing her in the forest.

It is obvious that Ragana and Baiga have conflicts.{nl}Their suggestion might seem like merit to us ultimately,{nl}but can't believe the demon's intention.{nl}Therefore, we shouldn't accept any temptation willingly.
On the other hand..{nl}It is dangerous to face all Beholder, Ragana, Baiga and the Baubas.
Unlike when you fought with Giltine,{nl}Ausrine is the only Goddess who preserves enough power to help you..{nl}But you will know that Ausrine doesn't want to be involved in this.
There is a way.
If you find the Mirtinas mined by the demons before them,{nl}you'll obviously have the initiative.{nl}Thus, let's hurry and find the Mirtinas Storage.
I need some time for recovery because I have spent a lot of power fighting with Ragana.
Sure.{nl}It won't take long to recover.
Keep in mind that we are still moving for each of our own responsibility.
I see..{nl}Gatves Highway is a path that leads into the forest.
We do need to go to Gatves Highway.
I still need more time.
We are just doing our own jobs anyway,{nl}so it's okay for you to go first.
Okay.{nl}I'll go after you as I get recovered.
There is Mirtinas crevice in the Gatves Highway.{nl}Go to Gatves Highway first.
I'll go after you as I get recovered.
Trace of wagon wheel is heading to the Issaugoti Forest.
I knew you would come this way.{nl}Too much power of Mirtinas is coming out from this deep forest.
Mirtinas Storage must be inside here{nl}It is true that it's an emergency,{nl}but things are getting bigger, we'd better go back to Laima's Sanctuary.
Okay,{nl}I'll see you again in Laima's Sanctuary.
Get ready..
Disaster is coming..
Humans will be destroyed..
Be careful..
Please..{nl}Be careful..
What you need to take with you..{nl}If you don't mind..{nl}Please Close your eyes..
I hope I can rest more.
Box with ominous energy coming out.{nl}Seems like keeping the mined Mirtinas.
Install the bomb in the box we've just found.
{nl}Seems like the bomb is well installed.
Saugumas Executor
Are you the thief who's after Beholder's precious Mirtinas?
From now on, I will execute the death penalty for the thief!
[Kingdom Reconstruction] Orsha Officer
You've heard about us?{nl}We've also heard about some rumors about you, Revelator.
We are gathered in the name of Kingdom Reconstruction.{nl}We've gathered to rebuild the collapsed kingdom and the world caused by the Medzio Diena.
Rather than relying on the disappearance of the Goddess, we should rebuild the kingdom on our own.
Ah, but don't get it wrong.{nl}We are people who are religious in Goddess.{nl}It is just that this situation may be the Goddess' will for human to be stronger by themselves.
So we, the Kingdom Reconstruction are dispatched to the world and doing their best to help the scene.
I've heard a lot about you Revelator.{nl}It would be a great help if you could help us.
Meet the members of Kingdom Reconstruction dispatched to each scene.{nl}They will need you.
[Kingdom Reconstruction] Orsha Soldier
If you help us, we'll surely repay for it accordingly.{nl}Your heroic story will spread out all over the world.
[Kingdom Reconstruction] Orsha Volunteer
The thing that can rebuild the continent in grief after the Medzio Diena is solidarity of humans.{nl}Soon, we will all fight to rebuild the kingdom.{nl}Please join us Revelator.
[Kingdom Reconstruction] Orsha Investigator
We, the Kingdom Reconstruction are continuously investigating the disaster scene to help the people in crisis.{nl}This place is also a mess.
[Kingdom Reconstruction] Orsha Medical Solider
We are doing our best, but it's heartbreaking to see the dying soldiers.{nl}Just wishing for their soul to go back to the Goddess Ausrine.
[Kingdom Reconstruction] Orsha Messenger
We need to keep in touch with the headquarters so that the soldiers are not abandoned in the battlefield.{nl}But it isn't easy to break the blockade.
